    <h1>Solar Power Electricity Project — Nigeria</h1>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>I led a solar electricity passion project to provide reliable power to local households in Nigeria. The aim was to enable extended study hours and improve quality of life.</p>

      <h2>What I did</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Coordinated procurement and installation of solar panels and batteries</li>
        <li>Worked with local stakeholders and volunteers to train maintenance procedures</li>
        <li>Documented outcomes and shared lessons to help a neighboring school adopt solar power</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Impact</h2>
      <p>Families reported additional study time each evening and improved access to lights and basic electronics; the project inspired wider adoption in the local education community.</p>
